org.universAAL.middleware.interfaces.configuration.scope

Class InstanceScope

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.middleware.interfaces.configuration.scope.Scope
      • org.universAAL.middleware.interfaces.configuration.scope.AALSpaceScope
        • org.universAAL.middleware.interfaces.configuration.scope.InstanceScope
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ModuleScope

    public class InstanceScope
extends AALSpaceScope
    Defines entity that are only applicable for the instance given in the scope. Entities with this scope will be shared in the whole AALSpaced, but stored only locally.
    Author:
    amedrano
